Description: Tools for systematic comparison of data frames, offering functionality to identify, 
    quantify, and extract differences. Provides functions with user-friendly and interactive 
    console output for immediate analysis, while also offering options to export differences as 
    structured data frames that can be easily integrated into existing workflows.
